title: Share
description: College student Masata Yuu is determined to protect classmate Saginuma Tatsuya! Saginuma is a famous actor who always has women fighting over him and stalking him, but he doesn't know how to handle the attention, so Masata moves in with him as a bodyguard. But will Masata be able to maintain the distance between them?
